### Shipping Service API Test File

### Create shipment
POST http://localhost:8084/api/shipping
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "orderId": 1,
  "recipientName": "John Doe",
  "recipientAddress": "123 Main St",
  "recipientCity": "New York",
  "recipientPostalCode": "10001",
  "recipientCountry": "USA",
  "carrier": "FedEx"
}

### Get shipment by ID
GET http://localhost:8084/api/shipping/1

### Get shipment by tracking number
GET http://localhost:8084/api/shipping/tracking/TRK-1234567890-123

### Get shipment by order ID
GET http://localhost:8084/api/shipping/order/1

### Get all shipments
GET http://localhost:8084/api/shipping

### Update shipment status
POST http://localhost:8084/api/shipping/1/status?status=SHIPPED

### Ship order
POST http://localhost:8084/api/shipping/order/1/ship

### Health Check
GET http://localhost:8084/actuator/health
